### Welcome to Hansiyang's Pages.
Hansiyang is a graduate student at [Xi'an Jiaotong University](http://www.xjtu.edu.cn/).

### Profile
* 2010 - 2014 [Xi'an Jiaotong University](http://www.xjtu.edu.cn/) bachelor degree
* 2011.08 - 2011.12 [City University of HongKong](http://www.cityu.edu.hk/cityu/index-sc.htm) exchange student
* 2013.07 - 2013. 09 [Microsoft Research Asia](http://www.msra.cn/zh-cn/default.aspx) intern
* 2014 - 2017 (expected) [Xi'an Jiaotong University](http://www.xjtu.edu.cn/) master degree

### Interest
* Algorithm
* Machine Learning
* Computer Vision

### Hobby
Jog Reading Cleaning
